sub_title: Head of Client Growth  at Zemanta, an Outbrain company
summary:
Isabel is Brazilian with Japanese, Italian, and German roots. She moved to Slovenia in 2015 with her husband and their three cats.
 Joined Zemanta in 2017 as a Customer Success Manager. In this role, Isabel was responsible for growing numerous global clients and played a key role in building successful relationships with agencies across the globe, including Publicis, Dentsu, Havas, OMG and WPP. In 2018, after Zemanta's Customer Success Team and client portfolio started growing at rapid speed, Isabel stepped in as a team lead for the European & International Market. 
When she's not playing tennis or running, you can find her cooking a delicious vegetarian meal, playing with her cats or answering the question "why Slovenia" for the seventy bajillionth time.
